<div class="row stagger-decrip ">
<div class="col-12 col-md-8 col-xl-6 px-5 py-3 py-lg-5 flex-center mb-md-3  sub-bg ml-auto">
<div class="my-3">
<h2 class="py-2 mb-0 text-left ">Conduct Education &amp; Training</h2>

<p class="text-left pb-3 ">&bull; Cooperated with Taichung City Labor Inspection Office and Central Taiwan University of Science and Technology to hold &ldquo;Taichung City OSH Disaster Prevention Technology Exhibition and Experience Activity&rdquo;, so employees could learn about the occupational hazards by this education and training.<br />
&bull; Conduct occupational safety and health on-the-job training</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
                                <!-- workplace-improved-reward -->
                                <div class="row ">
<div class="col-12 col-md-8 col-xl-9 px-0  ml-auto"><picture class="ratio-box ratio-16-5"> <source data-srcset="/storage/images/csr/workplace/picture-10.jpg" media="(min-width: 481px)" /> <source data-srcset="/storage/images/csr/workplace/picture-10.jpg" media="(max-width: 480px)" /> <img alt="" class="lazyload img-fluid" data-src="/storage/images/csr/workplace/picture-10.jpg" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhEAAFAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAAQAAUAAAIIjI+py+0PTQEAOw==" style="" title="" /> </picture></div>
</div>

<div class="row stagger-decrip ">
<div class="col-12 col-md-8 col-xl-6 px-5 py-3 py-lg-5 flex-center mb-md-3  main-bg mr-auto">
<div class="my-3">
<h2 class="py-2 mb-0 text-left white-text">Safety &amp; Health Improvement Award</h2>

<p class="text-left pb-3 white-text">&bull; Monthly 6S assessment is carried out, and the unit which wins first place for two months would earn the bonus so as to increase the awareness and participation of frontline workers.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
                                <!-- workplace-improved-conditions -->
                                <div class="row ">
<div class="col-12 col-md-8 col-xl-9 px-0 "><picture class="ratio-box ratio-16-5"> <source data-srcset="/storage/images/csr/workplace/picture-11.jpg" media="(min-width: 481px)" /> <source data-srcset="/storage/images/csr/workplace/picture-11.jpg" media="(max-width: 480px)" /> <img alt="" class="lazyload img-fluid" data-src="/storage/images/csr/workplace/picture-11.jpg" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhEAAFAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAAQAAUAAAIIjI+py+0PTQEAOw==" style="" title="" /> </picture></div>
</div>

<div class="row stagger-decrip ">
<div class="col-12 col-md-8 col-xl-6 px-5 py-3 py-lg-5 flex-center mb-md-3  sub-bg ml-auto">
<div class="my-3">
<h2 class="py-2 mb-0 text-left ">Working Conditions Improvement</h2>

<p class="text-left pb-3 ">&bull; The static eliminator is installed on the dump barrel of preform neck crystallization machines to prevent workers from injury caused by the static electricity spark.<br />
&bull; In the workplace of the label plants where are closed with negative pressure, the concentration of organic solvents was reduced. According to the result of environmental monitoring, the figure of organic solvents has indeed decreased.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
                            </div>
