        style="" />
</picture>
                            </a>
                            <h5 class="dark-grey-text text-center font-weight-500 py-2">
                                Install static eliminator to remove static electricity
                            </h5>
                        </div>
                                                                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
                        <!-- workplace-disaster-stat -->
                        <section class="py-5 gray-bg">
<div class="container mt-5">
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-10 col-12 mx-auto mb-3 text-center">
<h2 class="font-weight-bold ">Occupational Accident Statistics</h2>

<p class="py-3">The primary common type of injury analyzed was clamp, rolling up, and fall in 2021. Therefore, to strengthen and enhance the work safety awareness of employees in the plant to reduce occupational disasters, and listed as Work Safety and Environmental Protection Month every March. Occupational safety personnel will promote the weekly morning meeting to establish and cultivate the proper occupational safety and disaster prevention concepts. Hope to reduce the occurrence of occupational disasters. If an employee meets with an occupational accident, the occupational health nurse and department manager will visit the employee irregularly for understanding his/her recovery and evaluating the activities of daily living; the Legal Affairs Office provides legal consultation services. Before the employee gets back to work, the occupational medicine doctor and department manager would make return-to-work assessments and change his/her working pattern.</p>
<a class="btn btn-gray btn-md ml-0 btn-main my-3 mr-3 waves-effect waves-light display-table mr-auto mr-lg-0 ml-auto " href="https://dlf9q0zq4dwf6.cloudfront.net/honchuan/csr-report/2.occupational_accident_statistics2021(en).pdf" role="button" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-chevron-right  mx-1"></i>Learn more </a></div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
                        <!-- workplace-osha-project -->
                        <section class="py-5">
<div class="container-fluid my-5">
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-10 col-12 mx-auto mb-3 text-center">
<h2 class="font-weight-bold ">Promote the Four Plans of the Occupational Safety and Health Administration</h2>
<a class="btn btn-gray btn-md ml-0 btn-main my-3 mr-3 waves-effect waves-light display-table mr-auto mr-lg-0 ml-auto " href="https://dlf9q0zq4dwf6.cloudfront.net/honchuan/csr-report/3.promote_the_four_plans_of_the_occupational_safety_and_health_administration-2021(en).pdf" role="button" target="_blank"><i class="fa fa-chevron-right  mx-1"></i>Learn more </a></div>
</div>

<div class="row px-0 ">
<div class="col-12 col-md-6 main-bg">
<div class="row"><picture class="w-100"> <source data-srcset="/storage/encoded_images/webp/csr/workplace/picture-12.webp" media="(min-width: 481px)" type="image/webp" /> <source data-srcset="/storage/encoded_images/webp_thumbnails/csr/workplace/picture-12.webp" media="(max-width: 480px)" type="image/webp" /> <source data-srcset="/storage/images/csr/workplace/picture-12.jpg" media="(min-width: 481px)" /> <source data-srcset="/storage/images/csr/workplace/picture-12.jpg" media="(max-width: 480px)" /> <img alt="picture-12" class="lazyload" data-src="/storage/images/csr/workplace/picture-12.jpg" src="null" title="picture-12" /> </picture></div>

<div class="row py-5 px-4 main-bg">
<div class="col-4 col-sm-2 col-md-4 col-lg-3 col-xl-2 mb-3 project-icon"><picture class="ratio-box ratio-1-1"> <source data-srcset="/storage/images/csr/workplace/icon-06.png" media="(min-width: 481px)" /> <source data-srcset="/storage/images/csr/workplace/icon-06.png" media="(max-width: 480px)" /> <img alt="" class="lazyload img-fluid" data-src="/storage/images/csr/workplace/icon-06.png" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" style="" title="" /> </picture></div>

<div class="col-lg-9 col-xl-10">
<h2 class="font-weight-bold white-text">Workplace Violence Prevention Plan</h2>

<p class="text-left white-text">To protect the rights of our employees and provide a working environment free from violence, THC takes appropriate preventive, corrective and punitive measures for workplace violence incidents.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="col-12 col-md-6 sub-bg">
<div class="row"><picture class="w-100"> <source data-srcset="/storage/encoded_images/webp/csr/workplace/picture-13.webp" media="(min-width: 481px)" type="image/webp" /> <source data-srcset="/storage/encoded_images/webp_thumbnails/csr/workplace/picture-13.webp" media="(max-width: 480px)" type="image/webp" /> <source data-srcset="/storage/images/csr/workplace/picture-13.jpg" media="(min-width: 481px)" /> <source data-srcset="/storage/images/csr/workplace/picture-13.jpg" media="(max-width: 480px)" /> <img alt="picture-13" class="lazyload" data-src="/storage/images/csr/workplace/picture-13.jpg" src="null" title="picture-13" /> </picture></div>

<div class="row py-5 px-4 sub-bg">
<div class="col-4 col-sm-2 col-md-4 col-lg-3 col-xl-2 mb-3 project-icon"><picture class="ratio-box ratio-1-1"> <source data-srcset="/storage/images/csr/workplace/icon-07.png" media="(min-width: 481px)" /> <source data-srcset="/storage/images/csr/workplace/icon-07.png" media="(max-width: 480px)" /> <img alt="" class="lazyload img-fluid" data-src="/storage/images/csr/workplace/icon-07.png" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" style="" title="" /> </picture></div>

<div class="col-lg-9 col-xl-10">
<h2 class="font-weight-bold ">Abnormal Workload Risk Management</h2>

<p class="text-left ">To prevent employees from the morbidity risk of working shifts, working at night, and long working hours,<br />
THC has made the&ldquo;Abnormal Workload Ailment Prevention Policy&rdquo;to protect the health and safety of our employees.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="col-12 col-md-6 main-bg">
<div class="row"><picture class="w-100"> <source data-srcset="/storage/encoded_images/webp/csr/workplace/picture-14.webp" media="(min-width: 481px)" type="image/webp" /> <source data-srcset="/storage/encoded_images/webp_thumbnails/csr/workplace/picture-14.webp" media="(max-width: 480px)" type="image/webp" /> <source data-srcset="/storage/images/csr/workplace/picture-14.jpg" media="(min-width: 481px)" /> <source data-srcset="/storage/images/csr/workplace/picture-14.jpg" media="(max-width: 480px)" /> <img alt="picture-14" class="lazyload" data-src="/storage/images/csr/workplace/picture-14.jpg" src="null" title="picture-14" /> </picture></div>

<div class="row py-5 px-4 main-bg">
<div class="col-4 col-sm-2 col-md-4 col-lg-3 col-xl-2 mb-3 project-icon"><picture class="ratio-box ratio-1-1"> <source data-srcset="/storage/images/csr/workplace/icon-08.png" media="(min-width: 481px)" /> <source data-srcset="/storage/images/csr/workplace/icon-08.png" media="(max-width: 480px)" /> <img alt="" class="lazyload img-fluid" data-src="/storage/images/csr/workplace/icon-08.png" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" style="" title="" /> </picture></div>

<div class="col-lg-9 col-xl-10">
<h2 class="font-weight-bold white-text">Prevention of Ergonomic Hazards</h2>

<p class="text-left white-text">To protect the health of employees, THC endeavor to prevent ergonomic hazards and musculoskeletal disorders in the workplace.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="col-12 col-md-6 sub-bg">
<div class="row"><picture class="w-100"> <source data-srcset="/storage/encoded_images/webp/csr/workplace/picture-15.webp" media="(min-width: 481px)" type="image/webp" /> <source data-srcset="/storage/encoded_images/webp_thumbnails/csr/workplace/picture-15.webp" media="(max-width: 480px)" type="image/webp" /> <source data-srcset="/storage/images/csr/workplace/picture-15.jpg" media="(min-width: 481px)" /> <source data-srcset="/storage/images/csr/workplace/picture-15.jpg" media="(max-width: 480px)" /> <img alt="picture-15" class="lazyload" data-src="/storage/images/csr/workplace/picture-15.jpg" src="null" title="picture-15" /> </picture></div>

<div class="row py-5 px-4 sub-bg">
<div class="col-4 col-sm-2 col-md-4 col-lg-3 col-xl-2 mb-3 project-icon"><picture class="ratio-box ratio-1-1"> <source data-srcset="/storage/images/csr/workplace/icon-09.png" media="(min-width: 481px)" /> <source data-srcset="/storage/images/csr/workplace/icon-09.png" media="(max-width: 480px)" /> <img alt="" class="lazyload img-fluid" data-src="/storage/images/csr/workplace/icon-09.png" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==" style="" title="" /> </picture></div>

<div class="col-lg-9 col-xl-10">
<h2 class="font-weight-bold ">Protecting and Managing Maternal Health</h2>

<p class="text-left ">In order to ensure the physical and mental well-being and occupational safety of pregnant, postpartum, and breastfeeding female employees,<br />
THC has established&ldquo; Regualions of the Maternity Health Protection at the Workplace .&ldquo;</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
                        <!-- workplace-health -->
                        <section class="py-5 gray-bg">
<div class="container mt-5">
<div class="row">
<div class="col-md-10 col-12 mx-auto mb-3 text-center">
<h2 class="font-weight-bold ">Health Promotion and Management</h2>

<p class="py-3">In accordance with the Regulations of the Labor Health Protection, THC contracts medical personnel and employs full-time occupational health nurses in workplace to provide healthcare management and service and assist employers matching workers in the appropriate work. They are in charge of planning and implementing health education, health promotion, and health guidance for employees, preventing workplace injuries and illnesses, and carrying out health consultation, hierarchical abnormal condition management of special health examinations, and first aid. In addition, they are responsible to assist employers and occupational safety and health personnel preventing work&ndash;related diseases and improving work environment so that the Company can protect the mental, physical, and social health of employees. Employee health and wellbeing matter to THC, so we provide annual health examination for all employees, and special health examinations are also provided for some units.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
